{"meta":{"title":"2 Néfi 14","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/14?lang=por","contentType":"text/html","audio":[{"mediaUrl":"https://media2.ldscdn.org/assets/scriptures/the-book-of-mormon-another-testament-of-jesus-christ//2013-06-045-2-nephi-14-64k-por.mp3","voice":{"name":"audio"}}],"pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"e2de28c28e2009889a66fe1951e14a52a4da4a47","data-aid":"124116591","data-aid-version":"2","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/14","itemscope":"","itemtype":"http://schema.org/Article","lang":"por","data-orig-id":"aad669ae4a699b9a203f7fc9917f29ecfb153d79","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"2 Néfi 14","description":"Sião e suas filhas serão redimidas e purificadas no dia do milênio — Comparar com Isaías 4. Aproximadamente 559–545 a.C."},"pageSocial":{"title":"2 Néfi 14","description":"Sião e suas filhas serão redimidas e purificadas no dia do milênio — Comparar com Isaías 4. Aproximadamente 559–545 a.C."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"124117005\" id=\"title_number1\">Capítulo 14</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"124117007\" id=\"study_summary1\">Sião e suas filhas serão redimidas e purificadas no dia do milênio — Comparar com <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/4?lang=por\">Isaías 4</a>. Aproximadamente 559–545 a.C.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124117011\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>E naquele dia sete mulheres lançarão mão de um homem, dizendo: Nós comeremos nosso próprio pão e vestir-nos-emos com nossos próprios vestidos; tão somente queremos ser chamadas pelo teu nome, para desfazer o nosso <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>opróbrio</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124117016\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>Naquele dia o <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>ramo</a> do Senhor será belo e glorioso; o fruto da terra será excelente e formoso para os que escaparem de Israel.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124117021\" id=\"p3\"><span class=\"verse-number\">3 </span>E acontecerá que aqueles que ficarem em Sião e os que permanecerem em Jerusalém serão chamados santos. Todos os que estiverem inscritos entre os vivos em Jerusalém —</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124117027\" id=\"p4\"><span class=\"verse-number\">4 </span><a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>Quando</a> o Senhor tiver <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>lavado</a> a imundície das filhas de Sião e limpado o sangue de Jerusalém do meio dela, com o espírito de justiça e com o espírito de <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>ardor</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124117030\" id=\"p5\"><span class=\"verse-number\">5 </span>E criará o Senhor, sobre toda a habitação do monte Sião e sobre as suas congregações, uma <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note5a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>nuvem</a> e uma fumaça de dia e o resplendor de um fogo chamejante à noite; porque sobre toda a glória de Sião haverá uma defesa.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124117033\" id=\"p6\"><span class=\"verse-number\">6 </span>E haverá um tabernáculo por sombra contra o calor do dia e por <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note6a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>refúgio</a> e esconderijo contra a tempestade e a chuva.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"14\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note1a\" data-full-marker=\"1a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124117036\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><small>IE</small> o estigma de não ter casado e não ter filhos.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"2\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note2a\" data-full-marker=\"2a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124117039\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/60.21?lang=por#p21\">Isa. 60:21</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.5?lang=por#p5\">2 Né. 3:5</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.25?lang=por#p25\">Jacó 2:25</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"4\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note4a\" data-full-marker=\"4a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124117042\" id=\"note4a_p1\"><small>IE</small> Quando o Senhor tiver purificado a Terra.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note4b\" data-full-marker=\"4b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124117046\" id=\"note4b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/wash-washed-washings?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Lavado, Lavamento, Lavar</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note4c\" data-full-marker=\"4c\">\n<p data-aid=\"124117050\" id=\"note4c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/3.2-3?lang=por#p2\">Mal. 3:2–3</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/4.1?lang=por#p1\">4:1</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"5\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note5a\" data-full-marker=\"5a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124117051\" id=\"note5a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ex/13.21?lang=por#p21\">Êx. 13:21</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"6\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note6a\" data-full-marker=\"6a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124117054\" id=\"note6a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/25.4?lang=por#p4\">Isa. 25:4</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/115.6?lang=por#p6\">D&amp;C 115:6</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","footnotes":{"note1a":{"id":"note1a","marker":"1a","pid":"124117011","context":"opróbrio","text":"<p data-aid=\"124117036\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><small>IE</small> o estigma de não ter casado e não ter filhos.</p>"},"note2a":{"id":"note2a","marker":"2a","pid":"124117016","context":"ramo","text":"<p data-aid=\"124117039\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/60.21?lang=por#p21\">Isa. 60:21</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.5?lang=por#p5\">2 Né. 3:5</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.25?lang=por#p25\">Jacó 2:25</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/60.21?lang=por#p21","text":"Isa. 60:21"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.5?lang=por#p5","text":"2 Né. 3:5"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.25?lang=por#p25","text":"Jacó 2:25"}]},"note4a":{"id":"note4a","marker":"4a","pid":"124117027","context":"Quando","text":"<p data-aid=\"124117042\" id=\"note4a_p1\"><small>IE</small> Quando o Senhor tiver purificado a Terra.</p>"},"note4b":{"id":"note4b","marker":"4b","pid":"124117027","context":"lavado","text":"<p data-aid=\"124117046\" id=\"note4b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/wash-washed-washings?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Lavado, Lavamento, Lavar</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/wash-washed-washings?lang=por","text":"GEE Lavado, Lavamento, Lavar"}]},"note4c":{"id":"note4c","marker":"4c","pid":"124117027","context":"ardor","text":"<p data-aid=\"124117050\" id=\"note4c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/3.2-3?lang=por#p2\">Mal. 3:2–3</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/4.1?lang=por#p1\">4:1</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/3.2-3?lang=por#p2","text":"Mal. 3:2–3"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/4.1?lang=por#p1","text":"4:1"}]},"note5a":{"id":"note5a","marker":"5a","pid":"124117030","context":"nuvem","text":"<p data-aid=\"124117051\" id=\"note5a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ex/13.21?lang=por#p21\">Êx. 13:21</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/ex/13.21?lang=por#p21","text":"Êx. 13:21"}]},"note6a":{"id":"note6a","marker":"6a","pid":"124117033","context":"refúgio","text":"<p data-aid=\"124117054\" id=\"note6a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/25.4?lang=por#p4\">Isa. 25:4</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/115.6?lang=por#p6\">D&amp;C 115:6</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/25.4?lang=por#p4","text":"Isa. 25:4"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/115.6?lang=por#p6","text":"D&amp;C 115:6"}]}}},"pids":[["124116591",{"key":"124116591"}],["124117005",{"key":"124117005"}],["124117007",{"key":"124117007"}],["124117011",{"key":"124117011"}],["124117016",{"key":"124117016"}],["124117021",{"key":"124117021"}],["124117027",{"key":"124117027"}],["124117030",{"key":"124117030"}],["124117033",{"key":"124117033"}],["124117036",{"key":"124117036"}],["124117039",{"key":"124117039"}],["124117042",{"key":"124117042"}],["124117046",{"key":"124117046"}],["124117050",{"key":"124117050"}],["124117051",{"key":"124117051"}],["124117054",{"key":"124117054"}]],"tableOfContentsUri":"/scriptures/bofm","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/14"}